notices.title: 2024 Season Kickoff
notices.content: Join us for the 2024 FRC Season Kickoff! We'll be meeting at Sydney Technical High School to watch the game reveal and start brainstorming.

notices.title: Regular Meetings Resume
notices.content: Regular team meetings will resume on Thursdays from 3:30 PM to 6:00 PM and Saturdays from 9:00 AM to 4:00 PM.
